'''小胖'''是因其头像被放置在众多人像中而成名的[[网络爆红|网络爆红]]。因此成名的上海男孩[[钱志君|钱志君]]成为了公众人物，随后小胖出演了多部电影。

==个人经历==
2003年上海[[金山区_(上海市)|金山区]]的学生[[钱志君|钱志君]]在某次交通安全集会上<ref name="heardround">"[http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,231223,00.html The Last Laugh on the Fat Joke Heard 'Round the World] {{Wayback|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,231223,00.html |date=20120305230039 }}." ''[[Fox_News|Fox News]]''. Tuesday November 21, 2006. Retrieved on May 10, 2011.</ref>与班级同学担任志愿者<ref name="Macartney">Macartney, Jane. "[http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/article644465.ece Face of 'Little Fatty' finds fame among China's web users] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/article644465.ece |date=20110523085105 }}." ''[[The_Times|The Times]]''. November 21, 2006. Retrieved on May 16, 2011.</ref>时一张被人拍摄的照片<ref name="Culturalrevolution">"[http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/the-new-cultural-revolution-how-little-fatty-made-it-big-424469.html The new cultural revolution: How Little Fatty made it big] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/the-new-cultural-revolution-how-little-fatty-made-it-big-424469.html |date=20110806062829 }}." ''[[The_Independent|The Independent]]''. Thursday November 16, 2006. Retrieved on May 18, 2011.</ref>流传到了猫扑网，成为了整个事件的导火索。从2003年开始，钱志君的脸被大量恶搞到名人、电影海报，游戏封面上<ref name="Madeit">{{cite news|date=2006-11-16 |author=Clifford Coonan |work=the Independent |url=http://news.independent.co.uk/world/asia/article1987610.ece |title=The new cultural revolution: How Little Fatty made it big |accessdate=2007-02-21 |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061119040505/http://news.independent.co.uk/world/asia/article1987610.ece |archivedate=2006-11-19 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |publisher=the Times online |author=Jane Macartney |date=2006-11-22 |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article644809.ece |title=A fat chance of saving face |accessdate=2007-02-21 |location=London |language=en |archive-date=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718123741/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article644809.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。出名后[[路透社|路透社]]以及《[[独立报|独立报]]》等外国媒体也对钱志君进行了报道。

==本人回应==
据钱志君说，当网络模因第一次出现时，钱学森的老师和同学为了不伤害他的感情，都避免提及这一现象。当他接受《上海日报》采访时，为了保护他的隐私，该报没有透露他的真实姓名。因此在真实信息被揭露很多网民误以为钱志君是广西南宁人。钱志君表示对他的恶搞能让网民感到欢乐使他很欣慰<ref name="heardround"/>。他不喜欢自己的脸被恶搞到裸体女人身上<ref name="IOL">"[http://www.iol.co.za/news/back-page/little-fatty-likes-his-newfound-fame-1.303302 'Little fatty' likes his newfound fame] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/back-page/little-fatty-likes-his-newfound-fame-1.303302 |date=20150924083320 }}." ''[[Independent_Online_(South_Africa)|IOL]]''. 2006-11-15. Retrieved on 2011-05-10.</ref>。

钱志君家人起初曾决定打官司，最终放弃并开始从恶搞带来的名声中获利。

